--- !u!114 &640947480
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 640947479}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: dab40134f96b0c04e893ef68ca62f8c8, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::GameManager01
  dialogue_text01: {fileID: 2130103972}
  character_text01: {fileID: 379653273}
  dialogue01:
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: ...Thanks for the drink.
    options: []
  - char_name: Vikram
    dialogue_text: You're welcome. Anyway, do you have any questions for me, "journalist"?
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: Uhm, is that a horn on your head?
    options: []
  - char_name: Vikram
    dialogue_text: Observant, are we? Indeed it is.
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: Does no one...question why?
    options: []
  - char_name: Vikram
    dialogue_text: Ah, people just assume it's part of my style. Who's going to question
      me?
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: ...Is it not part of your style?
    options: []
  - char_name: Vikram
    dialogue_text: You ask that like you don't already know.
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: Let me guess, I said in the letter that I aleady know?
    options: []
  - char_name: Vikram
    dialogue_text: There you go! Finally, not in denial. Don't worry, I'd be starstruck
      too if I was in your position.
    options: []
  - char_name: Vikram
    dialogue_text: Not only do you get to meet a Unicorn, you also get to meet Vikram!
      I think I'd swoon!
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: I'm sorry, a what now?
    options: []
  - char_name: Vikram
    dialogue_text: Hm? You're the one who pointed out my horn, and if you look at
      my ears, I think it makes it obvious.
    options: []
  - char_name: Vikram
    dialogue_text: I'm a Unicorn.
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: ...No.
    options: []
  - char_name: Vikram
    dialogue_text: What do you mean "no"?
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: I mean, no you're not. Unicorns are horses... you look... human...
    options: []
  - char_name: Vikram
    dialogue_text: Ah, that's a common misonception about us non-human creatures.
      We integrated into human society quite nicely, some of us just need to hide
      more features than others.
    options: []
  - char_name: Vikram
    dialogue_text: Lucky for me, everyone takes me for one with a bold sense of style,
      so people just assume it's my choice to wear a horn.
    options: []
  - char_name: Vikram
    dialogue_text: Very gullible, you folk are.
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: But I mean, you have horse ears...so you must have been some form
      of horse at some point...
    options: []
  - char_name: Vikram
    dialogue_text: We adapted, darling. With humans being increasingly more populous,
      we had to. Not that I'm complaining. You're all soo cute~
    options: []
  - char_name: characterText
    dialogue_text: Uh... thank you?
    options: []
  - char_name: 
    dialogue_text: ...
    options: []
  line_index01: 0
  continue_button01: {fileID: 1238595497}
  next_scene01: {fileID: 29809295}
  pause_screen01: {fileID: 48979235}
  journal01: {fileID: 647382385}
